Package: assignment1
Title: Cycling Infrastructure Analysis Using OpenStreetMap Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrea Belen", "Cretu Toma", email = "al415615@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to download, classify, and visualize cycling infrastructure data from OpenStreetMap. It builds spatial cycling networks, classifies infrastructure types, computes summary statistics, and generates maps and plots for spatial data analysis using vector-based data cubes.
